          class="lang-en-gb">Some early development screen shots of a UTF-8 development version MKDoc with Punjabi templates.</dd>

        <dt xml:lang="en-gb" lang="en-gb" 
          class="lang-en-gb"><a href="http://mkdoc.com/news/mkdoc-1-2/" 
          hreflang="en-gb">MKDoc version 1.2</a>
        </dt>
        <dd xml:lang="en-gb" lang="en-gb" 
          class="lang-en-gb">MKDoc 1.2 has just been added to the downloads site. It has new features, better speed and  bug-fixes. Be sure to check it out!</dd>

